\fs24 \cf0 3 clients ($4,500/mo):
\f1\b0  Comfortable. Keep pipeline active. Build case studies. Start raising prices for new clients.\

\f0\b 5 clients ($7,500/mo):
\f1\b0  Full but manageable. Slow pipeline. Raise prices 15-20% for new clients. Start identifying delegation candidates.\

\f0\b 6-7 clients ($10K+/mo):
\f1\b0  At capacity. Stop at current pricing. Raise new clients to $2K-$2.5K. Hire first contractor. Pipeline = maintenance/referrals only.\

\f0\b 8+ clients ($14K+/mo):
