\f1  tag client si est\'e1 de acuerdo.\
4. **Referral ask** (Week 2, after positive signal): "Is there anyone in your network dealing with [specific problem]? I have room for 1 more client this quarter."\
5. **Process refinement** (Week 3): \'bfQu\'e9 parte de este proyecto tard\'f3 m\'e1s de lo esperado? Refinar prompt o template correspondiente.\
6. **Portfolio update** (Week 4): A\'f1adir case study al website. Actualizar "Recent Work" en LinkedIn.\
7. **Outbound intelligence** (Ongoing): El research de ESTE cliente revel\'f3 competidores, market trends, o companies que son ICP para OTROS proyectos 
